I had to make my own way.

47
00:03:52,315 --> 00:03:54,931
So I decided to leave home

48
00:03:55,110 --> 00:03:57,146
and join the circus.

49
00:03:57,320 --> 00:04:00,608
- What do you want?
- A job on your next film.

50
00:04:00,782 --> 00:04:02,192
You're an actor, aren't you?

51
00:04:02,367 --> 00:04:03,948
No, I want to work
on the production side.

52
00:04:04,119 --> 00:04:06,326
We don't start shooting
for another eight weeks.

53
00:04:06,496 --> 00:04:09,988
- Come back nearer the time.
- May I wait until there's a job?

54
