for 18 weeks.

109
00:07:07,844 --> 00:07:10,176
- My wife would never agree.
- That's a pity, Mr. Cotes-Preedy.

110
00:07:10,347 --> 00:07:12,679
I'll have to tell Miss Monroe
to look elsewhere, then.

111
00:07:12,849 --> 00:07:16,262
- Marilyn Monroe?
- Yes.

112
00:07:16,436 --> 00:07:20,054
Suppose I'd have to be introduced.

113
