Who built this place?
Hansel and Gretel?

116
00:07:42,879 --> 00:07:44,870
It's one of the best houses
in the area.

117
00:07:45,048 --> 00:07:46,959
All right. We'll take it.

118
00:07:47,133 --> 00:07:49,715
But ditch the wallpaper.
It's giving me a migraine.

119
00:07:52,806 --> 00:07:55,013
That house was perfect for Marilyn.

120
00:07:55,183 --> 00:07:57,174
- Can't use it now.
- Yes, we can.

121
