124
00:08:04,526 --> 00:08:07,233
So the other one, Parkside,
is much better.

125
00:08:07,404 --> 00:08:08,894
And the owner is very discreet.

126
00:08:09,072 --> 00:08:11,905
So we've got two expensive houses now
