- Let's see to it, Hughie.

133
00:08:28,717 --> 00:08:30,207
Well done, boy.

134
00:08:31,594 --> 00:08:33,425
Nice job, kid.

135
00:08:37,225 --> 00:08:39,432
Colin Clark,
Laurence Olivier Productions.

136
00:08:44,441 --> 00:08:46,898
