Here. Come here. Let me warm you up.

1002
01:04:32,994 --> 01:04:35,451
Is that better?

1003
01:04:37,791 --> 01:04:41,750
I want this to be the perfect date.

1004
01:04:41,920 --> 01:04:45,504
I haven't had a real date
since I was 13 years old.

1005
01:05:01,940 --> 01:05:03,601
That was nice.

1006
01:05:06,569 --> 01:05:11,029
Ahem! Time to go home,
I think, Miss Monroe.

1007
01:05:27,549 --> 01:05:30,336
Be careful not
