Well, whatever it was you did
to her, boy, keep doing it.

1120
01:16:00,347 --> 01:16:05,683
I've never seen her so happy.

1121
01:16:05,853 --> 01:16:07,434
- Yes.
- We need Colin

1122
01:16:07,605 --> 01:16:09,015
at the house right away.

1123
01:16:09,190 --> 01:16:11,146
Got a pain in my side,
for Christ's sake.

1124
01:16:11,317 --> 01:16:13,979
What are they trying to make me
think I'm crazy or something?

1125
01:16:14,153 --> 01:16:18,066
Is that what it is? You know I don't
just rev it up like a Model T.

1126
01:16:18,240 --> 01:16:20,322
I don't just crank it up.

1127
01:16:20,493 --> 01:16:23,360
No one's asking you to just crank it up.
We're worried about you...

1128
01:16:23,537 --> 01:16:25,778
Isn't that what you're saying?
I was sick, for God's sake!

1129
01:16:25,956 --> 01:16:28,447
- Can I be sick?
- Colin's here.

1130
01:16:28,626 --> 01:16:29,741
Colin.

1131
01:16:30,795 --> 01:16:32,285
Colin.

1132
01:16:33,339 --> 01:16:36,456
Colin thinks I'm a good actress.
Don't you, Colin?

1133
01:16:36,634 --> 01:16:38,750
- Yes I do. You were wonderful today.
- See?

1134
