Forget Marilyn Monroe.

1177
01:20:12,725 --> 01:20:14,465
Forget Hollywood. Let it all go.

1178
01:20:16,979 --> 01:20:18,469
Just let it go.

1179
01:20:24,570 --> 01:20:26,026
I couldn't just give it up.

1180
01:20:27,906 --> 01:20:29,487
Why not?

1181
01:20:31,744 --> 01:20:33,905
Why not, when it drives you crazy?

1182
01:20:34,079 --> 01:20:36,035
